<DOCNO>GH951201-000085</DOCNO>
<DOCID>GH951201-000085</DOCID>
<DATE>951201</DATE>
<HEADLINE>AMEC replies</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>1</EDITION>
<PAGE>23</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>975110351</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
CONSTRUCTION and engineering group AMEC said yesterday that the #1-a-share bid
for the company by Norwegian industrial engineering group Kvaerner undervalued
its assets. In a statement, AMEC said: ``Kvaerner clearly recognises the
attraction of AMEC's process and energy activities,'' adding, ``its offer,
however, does not recognise their value.''
</TEXT>
